hero_translation.tips_hero_translation_1: The heroes below will be consumed.
hero_translation.tips_hero_translation_2: The heroes to be consumed must be either Empire/Woodland/Eclipse or Divine/Demon.
hero_translation.tips_hero_translation_3: Conversion yields heroes different from the ones consumed.
hero_translation.tips_hero_translation_4: Obtain by converting excess E/W/E heroes.
hero_translation.tips_hero_translation_5: Obtain by converting excess D/D heroes.
